<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The documentation for the <a href="http://framework.zend.com/manual/en/zend.controller.actionhelpers.html#zend.controller.actionhelpers.contextswitch">ContextSwitch helper</a> states the XML context will set the content-type response header to {{text/xml}}.</p>

<p>This is incorrect as the code actually sets the header to {{application/xml}}.</p>

<p>See Zend/Controller/Action/Helper/ContextSwitch.php:149</p>

